Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.36,0:00:03.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) "Quan m'he despertat m'he trobat lligat de peus i mans
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:05.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,i a les fosques."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:09.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Havíem quedat per anar a comprar\Nun joc nou amb els meus amics."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:13.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Però pel camí he vist\Nque algú forçava una caixa forta."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:18.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Estava amagat,\Nperò m'ha descobert."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:22.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"M'ha pegat i m'ha tancat\Na dins d'un taüt."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:25.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Mentrestant, en Kogoro treballa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:29.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"en el cas del testament desaparegut\Nde l'empresari Gotaro Karahashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:32.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,que es va morir fa tres dies."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:35.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Investiga qui el pot haver robat."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.36,0:00:38.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Per sort, finalment he aconseguit comunicar-me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:41.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,amb la Lliga de Detectius Júnior\Namb el transmissor."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:45.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"I llavors he notat\Nque la caixa es començava a moure."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:51.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ikusen no meikyuu de\Nikusen no nazo wo toite.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:54.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Hontou no boku modoreta nara.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:57.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kono himitsu subete\Nwo tsutaetai nda.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:00.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"El cel contempla\Nels laberints del món."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:02.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Una gran perspicàcia resol\Ntots els misteris."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:06.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"En Conan està atrapat a les fosques\Ni no veu la manera de sortir-ne."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:08.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La veritat sempre s'acaba sabent."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:12.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Sembla un nen, però té el cervell d'un adult i és el detectiu Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:21.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sora wo sabishige ni\Nmiageru kimi wo miteru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:30.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,Boku wa mabataki mo\Nwakaru hodo soba ni iru no ni.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:37.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sugu soko made semaru kyoui\Nfukaku naru yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:42.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,Mebiusu no wa mawari tsudzuke nukedasenakute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:44.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kotae wa doko ni?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:50.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ikusen no meikyuu de\Nikusen no nazo wo toite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:55.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,Chikaku ni ite demo tookute\Nkimi to majiwaranai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:02:00.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,Itsu made mo tsudzuku\Nfutashika na mirai demo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:05.44,Songs,,0,0,0,,Mada mienai deguchi motome\Nhashiri tsudzukeru kara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:10.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,Donna ni mayotte mo\Nkimi wo mitsukeru kara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:13.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Hontou no boku modoreta nara.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:16.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kono omoi subete\Nwo tsutaetai nda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:21.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:27.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"En Conan, atrapat a les fosques\N(Segona part)".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.88,White,,0,0,0,,Digue'ns què passa, Conan?\NConan, em sents?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:36.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(transmissor) "Un cotxe...,\Nel taüt és a dins d'un cotxe."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Un cotxe fúnebre."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:41.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:41.24,White,,0,0,0,,(tots) Un cotxe fúnebre?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:45.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"He sentit olor d'encens,\Ni l'aire fred del gel sec."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"N'estic seguríssim."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:51.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Soc a dins d'un taüt,\Nen un doble fons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:55.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Per tant, això vol dir...\Nque sobre meu hi ha el cos d'algú.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:58.68,White,,0,0,0,,-Hem d'anar a buscar-lo de seguida!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:58.68,White,,0,0,0,,-(tots tres) Què?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:01.20,White,,0,0,0,,Si és un cotxe fúnebre,\Nno ens costarà gaire trobar-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:04.40,White,,0,0,0,,-Jo no ho tinc clar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:04.40,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, és veritat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:08.80,White,,0,0,0,,Avui dia la majoria de cotxes fúnebres són cotxes normals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:11.28,White,,0,0,0,,Ja no en queden gaires,\Ncom els d'abans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:14.08,White,,0,0,0,,Per tant, no serà fàcil de trobar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:16.40,White,,0,0,0,,Val més que truquem\Na la policia de seguida.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:18.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Espera't, Ai!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:20.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,La policia necessitarà\Nmés informació.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:24.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,És probable que el lloc\Non era abans fos una funerària.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:26.48,White,,0,0,0,,(Ai) "Entesos. Ja ho miro."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:26.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No m'estranyaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.52,White,,0,0,0,,Val més que ens les repartim,\Nper trucar-hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:37.32,White,,0,0,0,,Si en trobem una on hagin fet\Nuna cerimònia fa poc...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:40.72,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, llavors sabrem\Nque en Conan és al cotxe fúnebre...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:42.80,White,,0,0,0,,que haurà sortit de la funerària.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:46.08,White,,0,0,0,,Si és així, voldrà dir que porten\Nen Conan..., que el porten cap a...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:49.04,White,,0,0,0,,-Cap al crematori?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:49.04,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí, que el porten cap al crematori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.76,White,,0,0,0,,Què?! Vols dir que porten\Nen Conan a incinerar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:54.04,White,,0,0,0,,Per això ens hem d'afanyar\Na trobar-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:06.36,White,,0,0,0,,-Aquesta tampoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:06.36,White,,0,0,0,,-No hi ha hagut sort. Aquesta no és.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:11.04,White,,0,0,0,,(tots tres) Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:11.04,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Nois!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.12,White,,0,0,0,,(Ayumi) Hola, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.84,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Perdoni, es podria esperar un moment, sisplau? No trigaré.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:19.72,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Estava molt preocupada, nois.\NOn és en Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:22.76,Cyan,,0,0,0,,I on és?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:22.76,White,,0,0,0,,Ja sabem on és, l'hem trobat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:25.16,White,,0,0,0,,De moment només sabem\Nque va en un cotxe fúnebre.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:28.24,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Un cotxe fúnebre? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:30.92,White,,0,0,0,,(tots) Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:30.92,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Vaja, però si és...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:33.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Un testament?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.80,White,,0,0,0,,(Mitsuhiko) Què?\NHa contractat en Kogoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:39.60,White,,0,0,0,,Segur que era\Nel bufet d'advocats Asada?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:42.88,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Sí. Aquest matí d'hora el pare\Nha vingut aquí per un cas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:46.16,White,,0,0,0,,(Mitsuhiko) Potser té a veure\Namb el robatori que ha dit en Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:48.92,White,,0,0,0,,Què t'hi jugues? Segur que sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.48,Cyan,,0,0,0,,El pare m'ha trucat fa una estona\Ni m'ha dit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.60,Cyan,,0,0,0,,que havia d'anar a un enterrament\Namb l'advocat del bufet Asada.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:57.92,Cyan,,0,0,0,,M'ha demanat que li portés el vestit dels enterraments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:00.40,White,,0,0,0,,(tots tres) Eh?\NQuè dius, un enterrament?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:04.68,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Sí... Sí que m'ha dit aquest nom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:04.68,White,,0,0,0,,I t'ha dit si era aquí?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:08.12,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Però què feu?\NOn aneu, tan de pressa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:11.96,White,,0,0,0,,-Hem de marxar de seguida.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:11.96,White,,0,0,0,,-Corre, puja, Ran, afanya't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.04,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.04,White,,0,0,0,,Va, puja, corre!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:19.84,White,,0,0,0,,Què? Però què dieu, ara? Com pot ser\Nque en Conan sigui a dins del taüt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:22.64,White,,0,0,0,,I, a més, dieu\Nque a dins també hi ha el testament?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.76,White,,0,0,0,,N'esteu ben segurs, del que dieu,\Nnois?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.88,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, perquè\Nés el que ens ha dit en Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:29.76,White,,0,0,0,,Ha dit que era a dins d'una capsa petita de fusta de paulònia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:31.84,White,,0,0,0,,Tenen raó, és la capsa\Ndel testament.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:34.24,White,,0,0,0,,-Visca.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:34.24,White,,0,0,0,,-Ho hem aconseguit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:37.56,White,,0,0,0,,S'ha acabat fa una estona.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:37.56,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Pare, quan és l'enterrament?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:40.96,White,,0,0,0,,El cotxe fúnebre i la família\Nja han marxat cap al crematori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:44.64,White,,0,0,0,,(tots tres) Hem arribat tard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:44.64,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Com, que ja han marxat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:46.52,White,,0,0,0,,-No m'ho puc creure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:46.52,White,,0,0,0,,-No pot ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.08,White,,0,0,0,,Perdoni!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:50.24,White,,0,0,0,,El culpable deu voler
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.60,White,,0,0,0,,que incinerin el testament\Njuntament amb el cos del difunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:54.96,White,,0,0,0,,Si al final no apareix el testament,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.40,White,,0,0,0,,els germans es repartiran la fortuna\Ndel seu pare
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.68,White,,0,0,0,,a parts iguals entre tots tres.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:04.12,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Com pots pensar en això, ara, pare?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:04.12,White,,0,0,0,,Hem de descobrir qui és el culpable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:06.56,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Que no veus que estan a punt\Nd'incinerar en Conan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.24,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, tens raó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:11.68,White,,0,0,0,,(Ai) El taüt del senyor Karahashi\Nés l'únic que ha sortit d'aquí, avui.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.52,White,,0,0,0,,He demanat que truquessin\Nal crematori per preguntar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.32,White,,0,0,0,,Els han dit que esperen el cotxe\Nd'un moment a l'altre,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:19.40,White,,0,0,0,,però que encara no hi han arribat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.52,White,,0,0,0,,Què?\NSi encara no hi han arribat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:25.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,On soc, dius?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:25.24,White,,0,0,0,,Escolta'm, Conan, on ets, ara?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ja m'agradaria saber-ho, ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:31.48,White,,0,0,0,,"Una altra vegada?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:31.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ens hem tornat a aturar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:35.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí, ens hem anat parant i avançant\Na poc a poc tota l'estona,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:37.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,a intervals d'un minut,\Nmés o menys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.84,White,,0,0,0,,Ara penso que potser triguen tant\Na arribar al crematori
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:44.00,White,,0,0,0,,perquè es van aturant en llocs\Non hi ha gent que coneixia el difunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.32,White,,0,0,0,,"El president era un home\Nmolt apreciat,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:49.76,White,,0,0,0,,tant als petits tallers\Ncom a les grans empreses."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:52.12,White,,0,0,0,,Llocs on la gent el coneixia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:55.00,White,,0,0,0,,Vol dir com ara sucursals i empreses\Ncol·laboradores del grup Karahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:57.12,White,,0,0,0,,-Comprovi-ho de seguida.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:57.12,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:59.20,White,,0,0,0,,Jo aniré directament al crematori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:02.60,White,,0,0,0,,Si es van aturant com diu,\Npotser hi arribarem abans que ells.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:05.68,White,,0,0,0,,Hola, inspector.\NTenim una emergència.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:08.96,White,,0,0,0,,-Sisplau, que hi arribem a temps!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:08.96,White,,0,0,0,,-Ja venim, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:11.16,White,,0,0,0,,No pot anar una mica més de pressa,\Nsisplau?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:26.24,White,,0,0,0,,Ja hi som.\NHem arribat abans que ells.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:29.96,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Pare..., no ho trobes estrany?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:32.36,White,,0,0,0,,(mòbil)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:35.56,White,,0,0,0,,-(mòbil)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:35.56,White,,0,0,0,,-Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:40.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Hola, senyor Mouri. Soc jo, l'Asada.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:40.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Soc en Mouri, digui'm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:44.36,White,,0,0,0,,La comitiva fúnebre ha fet una parada\Nen una de les nostres filials.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:47.48,White,,0,0,0,,Però com que és cap de setmana\Ni hi ha molt de trànsit,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:49.56,White,,0,0,0,,han decidit no fer cap més visita.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:52.24,White,,0,0,0,,Aniran directes al crematori\Nsense fer més parades.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:54.32,White,,0,0,0,,-Aaa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:54.32,White,,0,0,0,,-I quan arribaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.40,White,,0,0,0,,Per l'hora que és,\Nja hi haurien de ser.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:58.48,White,,0,0,0,,O si no, deuen estar a punt\Nd'arribar-hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:00.76,White,,0,0,0,,-Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:00.76,White,,0,0,0,,-(Ai) Mireu què hi diu, aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:03.92,Cyan,,0,0,0,,A l'edifici annex?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:10.36,White,,0,0,0,,-(tots) Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:10.36,White,,0,0,0,,-Deu ser l'edifici d'aquí al costat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:32.36,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Esperin-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:32.36,White,,0,0,0,,Esperin-se, un moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:34.44,White,,0,0,0,,(tots) Conan! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:39.48,White,,0,0,0,,Com? Que volen\Nque anul·lem la incineració?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:41.72,White,,0,0,0,,Per què l'hauríem d'anul·lar?\NNo ho entenc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:44.16,White,,0,0,0,,Aquest detectiu\Nno té ni idea de res.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:46.48,Cyan,,0,0,0,,En Conan és a dins del taüt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:49.56,Cyan,,0,0,0,,A dins del taüt hi ha un nen,\Nhan d'aturar la incineració!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:54.60,White,,0,0,0,,Mm? Per la cara que han fet tots, sembla que sàpiguen de què parlem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:58.44,White,,0,0,0,,-Com volen que hi hagi un nen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:58.44,White,,0,0,0,,-Esclar que no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:01.04,White,,0,0,0,,I ara, quina bestiesa!\NNo pot ser.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:04.28,Green,,0,0,0,,Així no els hi farà res que obrim\Nel taüt per inspeccionar-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:07.32,White,,0,0,0,,L'esperàvem, inspector. Endavant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.40,Green,,0,0,0,,Soc l'inspector Megure,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:11.56,Green,,0,0,0,,de la Policia Metropolitana\Nde Tòquio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.64,0:09:13.68,Green,,0,0,0,,Podríem estar parlant\Nd'un cas de segrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.76,White,,0,0,0,,(tots dos) Sí, senyor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.76,Green,,0,0,0,,Takagi, Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:22.64,White,,0,0,0,,Encara que siguin de la policia,\Nno ho poden fer, això.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.08,Green,,0,0,0,,S'hi oposa per alguna raó\Nen concret?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.60,White,,0,0,0,,No, no, per res.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:32.96,Cyan,,0,0,0,,És a sota, en Conan, al doble fons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:35.36,White,,0,0,0,,Amb permís. Perdó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:35.36,Green,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.76,White,,0,0,0,,-(tots) Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.76,White,,0,0,0,,-Aquí no hi és!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:51.04,White,,0,0,0,,De fet, aquest taüt no té doble fons.\NHo hem comprovat. Aquí no hi ha res.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:54.40,Cyan,,0,0,0,,I ara què?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:54.40,White,,0,0,0,,Què diu? Com pot ser?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:10:01.00,White,,0,0,0,,És que no ho entenc, inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:10:01.00,Green,,0,0,0,,Em pots explicar què passa, Kogoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.56,White,,0,0,0,,A veure, ens poden explicar\Nquè passa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.32,White,,0,0,0,,Per què ens demana explicacions\Na nosaltres?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:09.12,White,,0,0,0,,Més aviat ens en haurien de donar\Nvostès.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:11.68,White,,0,0,0,,Qui es farà responsable\Ndel que ha passat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:15.04,Green,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Ja-ja en parlarem més endavant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:15.04,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:18.40,White,,0,0,0,,Conan, em sents?\NDigue'm on ets, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:20.48,White,,0,0,0,,-(transmissor: interferència)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:20.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Conan, em sents?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:24.64,White,,0,0,0,,-Què li deu haver passat? On deu ser?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:24.64,White,,0,0,0,,-Com és que no et contesta?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.52,White,,0,0,0,,Pobre Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ai, em sents? Ai, em sents?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:33.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ostres, tu! Es pot saber on anem?\NOn em porteu, ara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:40.24,White,,0,0,0,,Quina carraca! El motor no pot més.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.32,White,,0,0,0,,He perdut molt de temps,\Namb tantes parades.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) Aquest soroll...\NEm sembla que podria ser..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:50.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ara ho entenc!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:57.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Conan) Ai, em sents?\NQue em sents?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:02.40,White,,0,0,0,,(Kogoro) Com? Què dius, ara?\NQue hi ha un altre cotxe fúnebre?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:05.84,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Sí, en Conan diu\Nque hi devia haver un altre cotxe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:09.84,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Li sembla que devia estar aparcat\Nen algun aparcament subterrani.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:12.92,White,,0,0,0,,(tots tres) Mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:12.92,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Què fan, ara? On són? Han marxat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:15.00,Green,,0,0,0,,Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:15.00,White,,0,0,0,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:17.08,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, senyor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:22.76,White,,0,0,0,,Bona tarda.\NParlo amb la funerària?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.52,Green,,0,0,0,,Un moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.24,White,,0,0,0,,No es pensin\Nque se'n poden anar tan de pressa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.32,White,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.32,Green,,0,0,0,,Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:34.52,White,,0,0,0,,Ho sento, no poden marxar fins que aclarim exactament què ha passat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:41.52,White,,0,0,0,,Inspector, confirmat\Nper la funerària:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:43.60,White,,0,0,0,,hi havia un altre cotxe fúnebre.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.80,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, senyor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.80,Green,,0,0,0,,Ah, sí? Un altre?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:48.88,White,,0,0,0,,És un cotxe fúnebre molt vell\Nque ja fa temps que no fan servir
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:51.00,White,,0,0,0,,i l'han portat a desballestar\Navui mateix.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:53.76,White,,0,0,0,,L'han tingut aparcat al soterrani fins avui.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:56.96,White,,0,0,0,,I on és, ara? Què n'han fet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:56.96,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Sí, ho sabia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:59.72,White,,0,0,0,,No ho saben. La persona\Nque se n'ha cuidat ara no hi és.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:02.16,White,,0,0,0,,(mòbil)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:02.16,Green,,0,0,0,,No pot ser, ho han de saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.24,White,,0,0,0,,(mòbil)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.24,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:08.40,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Hola, Ai, per què heu marxat?\NDes d'on em truques, ara?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:12.16,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Què? Seguiu el cotxe fúnebre\Nen què va en Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.88,Green,,0,0,0,,Què?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.88,White,,0,0,0,,Què dius?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:21.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ara ho entenc. Aquest cotxe\Nl'havien de portar a desballestar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:25.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Acabem de girar a la dreta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:25.20,White,,0,0,0,,(rodes xerriquen: iii)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:28.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I ara a l'esquerra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:28.32,White,,0,0,0,,(rodes xerriquen: iii)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ara tot recte.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.36,White,,0,0,0,,(rodes xerriquen: iii)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:35.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Un altre cop a l'esquerra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:35.36,White,,0,0,0,,(rodes xerriquen: iii)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.00,White,,0,0,0,,Gir a la dreta i gir a l'esquerra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:40.08,White,,0,0,0,,Després tot recte\Ni un altre gir a l'esquerra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:42.60,White,,0,0,0,,-No el podem perdre!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:42.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Ho ha sentit, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:46.08,White,,0,0,0,,Així doncs, l'encens, el gel sec,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.32,White,,0,0,0,,les caixes de cartró\Ni la capsa de fusta...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.72,White,,0,0,0,,Totes les altres coses de dins\Ntambé són per llençar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:54.04,White,,0,0,0,,Són deixalles\Nque han deixat al cotxe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.72,White,,0,0,0,,No ets a dins d'un taüt,\Ncom et pensaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:13:01.28,White,,0,0,0,,"I el cotxe no anava tan lent\Npels coneguts del difunt."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:06.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,És un cotxe molt vell i no va bé.\NTot plegat ha sigut una casualitat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:10.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Em sembla... que per fi començo\Na entendre una mica aquest cas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:13.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Per fi començo a veure\Nles coses clares.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:18.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Hi havia més d'un culpable,\Nobrint la caixa, aquest matí."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.92,White,,0,0,0,,Així, no era un i prou?\NEra per això...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.24,White,,0,0,0,,"Eh? Però tots tenen coartada!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Perquè suposo que...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:37.40,White,,0,0,0,,S'han trobat a l'escenari del crim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:37.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I mentrestant...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:47.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "Vol obrir\Nla caixa forta."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:51.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "Oh!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:51.76,White,,0,0,0,,(cop: pom)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:59.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí, segur que ha anat així.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:02.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ens hem aturat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:02.24,White,,0,0,0,,(rodes xerriquen: iii)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:05.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Se sent un semàfor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:05.80,White,,0,0,0,,(pip discontinu)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:09.16,White,,0,0,0,,(pip discontinu)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:12.64,White,,0,0,0,,Després de sortir de la funerària,\Nhan passat per un túnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.72,White,,0,0,0,,Després dreta, esquerra, esquerra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:17.80,White,,0,0,0,,I ara han arribat\Na un pas de vianants amb semàfor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:22.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ens movem."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:22.08,White,,0,0,0,,Uf, n'hi ha moltíssims.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.80,White,,0,0,0,,(senyal acústic intermitent)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Som en un pas a nivell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:31.20,White,,0,0,0,,(Ai) "Un pas a nivell?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:35.16,White,,0,0,0,,Un pas a nivell... Ja l'he trobat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:38.44,White,,0,0,0,,-(tots) Que bé!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:38.44,White,,0,0,0,,-Ja sé on és, ja ho he trobat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:44.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ja està, l'he tallat.\NJa em puc deslligar del tot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:49.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ens hem tornat a parar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:55.28,White,,0,0,0,,(motor: s'atura)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:55.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però ara ha parat el motor del tot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:57.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Això deu voler dir\Nque ja hem arribat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:00.40,Green,,0,0,0,,Van cap al desballestador\Nde Kuriniji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:03.28,White,,0,0,0,,(policia: sirena)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:03.28,Green,,0,0,0,,De pressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:06.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:06.04,White,,0,0,0,,(cop sec: pom)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:10.76,White,,0,0,0,,(cop sec: pom)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ja està.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:26.20,White,,0,0,0,,(vehicle: estrèpit metàl·lic)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:26.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Aaaah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:35.16,White,,0,0,0,,-On ets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:35.16,White,,0,0,0,,-(Ayumi) Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.20,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.20,White,,0,0,0,,-Mireu allà dalt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.32,White,,0,0,0,,(policia: sirena)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.92,White,,0,0,0,,No, no pot ser! Conan, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:50.52,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:50.52,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:54.88,White,,0,0,0,,Pari la màquina!\NAturi la premsa! Pari-laaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Pari la màquina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:05.52,Cyan,,0,0,0,,No..., no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:05.52,Green,,0,0,0,,Oh, hem arribat massa tard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:11.68,White,,0,0,0,,No pot ser! No pot ser...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:21.04,White,,0,0,0,,No, no pot ser... Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:25.60,White,,0,0,0,,No..., no! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:31.68,White,,0,0,0,,Conan, si surts d'aquí sota\Net convido a... deu bols d'arròs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:36.36,White,,0,0,0,,(tots tres) Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:36.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No podria menjar tant ni de broma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:43.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:47.92,White,,0,0,0,,-(tots dos) Conan, estàs bé!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:47.92,White,,0,0,0,,-Has sortit, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:51.00,White,,0,0,0,,-Mm? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:51.00,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:53.04,Green,,0,0,0,,Sí!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:03.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Oh... M'ha anat de ben poc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:11.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ho he de fer ara, vinga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,He-he-he-he!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:24.28,White,,0,0,0,,Aaah...!\NOn és, el testament, on és?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:27.04,White,,0,0,0,,No pot ser que l'hagin esclafat\Ni destrossat amb el cotxe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:29.56,Cyan,,0,0,0,,On s'ha ficat, en Conan?\NNo el veig.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:36.56,White,,0,0,0,,Oh! On, on és el testament?\NOn és? Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.84,White,,0,0,0,,Ah..., ah..., oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:42.36,White,,0,0,0,,Hi ha novetats?\NHan trobat el testament?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:45.20,White,,0,0,0,,-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:45.20,White,,0,0,0,,-L'han trobat o què?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.96,White,,0,0,0,,En-en Kogoro Dorment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:57.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Conan) Hola!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:57.20,White,,0,0,0,,(veu Kogoro) Ara, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:01.52,White,,0,0,0,,Gràcies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:01.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,La capsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:06.48,White,,0,0,0,,-(tots) Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:06.48,White,,0,0,0,,-És l'últim testament.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:09.08,White,,0,0,0,,Aquest testament inclou els canvis
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:11.16,White,,0,0,0,,que va voler fer el president\Nabans de morir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.16,White,,0,0,0,,(veu Kogoro) Vaja, vaja...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:18.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Què?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:18.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Quina decepció, oi, Eisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:21.64,White,,0,0,0,,Xiclet, dius?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:21.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ha trepitjat xiclet, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:27.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Se sent l'olor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I el telèfon està ben enganxifós,\Nde quan l'ha trepitjat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:37.48,White,,0,0,0,,Què? No sé de què parla...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:40.32,White,,0,0,0,,(veu Kogoro) I el germà gran\Ni la germana,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:42.44,White,,0,0,0,,en Kozo i la Mitsuyo, també hi eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:46.36,White,,0,0,0,,Ens volien fer creure que són\Ntres germans molt mal avinguts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.24,White,,0,0,0,,i que no se suporten,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:51.44,White,,0,0,0,,perquè suposéssim que no es voldrien confirmar mútuament les coartades.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:54.12,White,,0,0,0,,Però és un truc molt vell\Ni no els ha sortit bé.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:58.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Exacte, no pot demostrar res.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:58.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Què diu? No en té cap prova!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.60,Green,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.60,White,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:04.00,White,,0,0,0,,Pot comprovar si hi ha empremtes,\Nal testament, sisplau?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.92,White,,0,0,0,,Si no m'equivoco\Ni la meva deducció és correcta,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:10.00,White,,0,0,0,,a més de les empremtes del difunt,\Ndel senyor Asada i d'en Conan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:12.60,White,,0,0,0,,també hi trobaran les empremtes\Ndels tres sospitosos.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:15.80,Green,,0,0,0,,És veritat, això?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:15.80,White,,0,0,0,,(tots dos) Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:20.60,White,,0,0,0,,Com que planejaven desfer-se\Ndel testament,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:23.48,White,,0,0,0,,l'han tocat tots sense pensar\Nque calgués posar-se guants.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:26.44,White,,0,0,0,,"Tenien pressa per comprovar-ne\Nel contingut
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:28.12,White,,0,0,0,,tan aviat com fos possible."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:30.12,White,,0,0,0,,No m'equivoco, oi que no?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:34.92,White,,0,0,0,,Segurament tots tres han conspirat
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:37.00,White,,0,0,0,,per aconseguir\Nque la fortuna del seu pare
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:39.12,White,,0,0,0,,es repartís entre vostès\Na parts iguals
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:41.24,White,,0,0,0,,o per tornar-lo a escriure\Na favor seu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:44.08,White,,0,0,0,,Han amagat el testament en un cotxe fúnebre que no es feia servir
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:46.28,White,,0,0,0,,i també hi han deixat tancat\Nen Conan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:48.40,White,,0,0,0,,pensant que el deixarien anar\Nmés tard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:50.48,White,,0,0,0,,Però no sabien que precisament avui
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:52.56,White,,0,0,0,,havien d'enviar el cotxe\Na desballestar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:56.24,White,,0,0,0,,Aaah... Oh,\Ntot això és culpa del pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:59.36,White,,0,0,0,,Sembla mentida,\Nno sé com se li va poder acudir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:03.12,White,,0,0,0,,Mira que deixar-l'hi tot\Na la seva secretària.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:07.32,White,,0,0,0,,-No es pot perdonar, una cosa així!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:07.32,White,,0,0,0,,-Deixar-l'hi tot a la seva amant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:12.04,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Com han pogut?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:17.16,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Com s'han atrevit a posar en perill\Nla vida d'un nen, d'en Conan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:22.80,Cyan,,0,0,0,,El que han fet vostès no,\Nque no es pot perdonar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:34.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:38.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,("Yesterday Love", Mai Kuraki)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:50.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:54.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kuyashii kedo soredemo omoi tsuzukete iku no deshou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:21:02.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Konna ni suki na hazu nanoni nakenai "jibun" ga iru naze?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:06.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ittai "watashi" wa "dare" de "nan" na no ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:09.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,"Hontou no jibun" sagashi ni ikitai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:16.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,"Koi" wa itsu no hi mo aoku setsunai misuterii.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:20.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,YESTERDAY LOVE, goodbye my LOVE,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:24.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,"Jibun" no yowasa to samishisa ni.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:27.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ima wo nigete ikun ja nai\Nhabataite ikun da
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:31.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,Koko kara sou tobitatsun da.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.48,0:21:34.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,YESTERDAY LOVE, goodbye my TEARS,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:38.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ichido shika nai jinsei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:43.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kako no jibun kara\N"ano sora" e tonde ikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:45.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Soshite tooku kara
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:50.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,"Kimi ga suki!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:54.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) "Al cap d'uns dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:56.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"el senyor Asada li va explicar\Na en Kogoro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:22:00.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"que havien entregat l'herència\Na la secretària del president,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.24,0:22:03.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,i ella n'havia fet donació\Na una entitat benèfica."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:07.20,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Quan hi penso...\NDeu haver sigut molt dur, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:10.08,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Estar tancat a les fosques\Nen un espai tan petit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.32,0:22:13.56,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Potser ara et farà por\Nanar al lavabo de nit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:15.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:15.80,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Si vols, t'hi puc acompanyar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:18.84,White,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:18.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No... no cal, Ran. Tranquil·la, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:22.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Que no cal, de veritat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:22.80,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Va, no et faci vergonya, home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:24.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(Shinichi, pensa) "Però què diu?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:24.84,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Que no em fa res!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:26.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Que ja vaig a l'institut, jo."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:31.44,White,,0,0,0,,Em demanes\Nque busqui un extraterrestre?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:32.76,White,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.04,0:22:35.48,White,,0,0,0,,Ho dic perquè el vaig veure\Namb els meus ulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:39.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Un ovni?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:39.08,White,,0,0,0,,Un objecte volador no identificat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.68,0:22:42.40,White,,0,0,0,,Fora d'aquí! No s'hi poden estar!\NOh! Senyor Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:45.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però, a veure, què deia l'home\Nque era al costat de la víctima?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:48.88,White,,0,0,0,,Segons ell, va sortir\Nun extraterrestre d'un ovni,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:52.04,White,,0,0,0,,va matar el senyor Nakatsu,\Nva tornar a l'ovni i se'n va anar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:54.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Conan) No us perdeu\Nel pròxim episodi:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:22:57.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Un cas d'ovnis difícil per l'inspector Chiba (Primera part)."
